OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1771909410
OL,3,CITV News taken inside Gaza tunnels as
OL,4,CIDF claims Hamas remains active
OL,6,FITV News is not normally allowed to
OL,7,Fenter the territory, but our Senior
OL,8,FInternational Correspondent, John
OL,9,FIrvine, was invited in by the Israeli
OL,10,Fmilitary. We were only allowed to film
OL,11,Funder its direction.
OL,13,FITV News has been taken inside Gaza
OL,14,Fand shown what Israel's military says
OL,15,Fis a Hamas-dug tunnel, which it claims
OL,16,Fproves the group remains an active
OL,17,Fforce.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
