OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1771909410
OL,3,CITV News taken inside Gaza tunnels as
OL,4,CIDF claims Hamas remains active
OL,6,FIsrael still controls large parts of
OL,7,Fthe Palestinian territory, following a
OL,8,Fceasefire in October, and its military
OL,9,Fhas continued its attacks.
OL,11,FFour months after the ceasefire was
OL,12,Fagreed, the only green shoots in Gaza
OL,13,Fare the weeds growing amid the rubble.
OL,15,FBrought in by the Israel Defence
OL,16,FForces (IDF), which controls the
OL,17,Feastern half of the enclave, there are
OL,18,Fonly Israeli soldiers here, no
OL,19,FPalestinians.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1771909410
OL,3,CITV News taken inside Gaza tunnels as
OL,4,CIDF claims Hamas remains active
OL,6,FThey are all hemmed into the western
OL,7,Fhalf, where, in places like Gaza City,
OL,8,Fthey are surrounded by rubble and
OL,9,Fbombed-out buildings.
OL,11,FWe were not close enough to see
OL,12,Fanyone, but we could hear the honking
OL,13,Fof car horns.
OL,15,FITV News is not normally allowed to
OL,16,Fenter the territory, but was invited
OL,17,Fin by Israeli forces, and we were only
OL,18,Fallowed to film under the direction of
OL,19,Fthe military.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1771909410
OL,3,CITV News taken inside Gaza tunnels as
OL,4,CIDF claims Hamas remains active
OL,6,FThe peace ushered in by October's
OL,7,Fceasefire was imperfect, and
OL,8,Fperiodically, we also heard machine
OL,9,Fgun fire coming from the yellow line,
OL,10,Fthe border cutting Gaza in two.
OL,11,FAttacks across it are frequent, and
OL,12,Fthe IDF remains alert.
OL,14,FThe situation is hardly conducive to
OL,15,Fre-construction and consequently, the
OL,16,Fruins all around are atrophying.
OL,18,FThe only building work we could see
OL,19,Fwas being done by the IDF. This hill
OL,20,Fand outpost weren't here the last time
OL,21,Fthat we were, back in November.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1771909410
OL,3,CITV News taken inside Gaza tunnels as
OL,4,CIDF claims Hamas remains active
OL,6,FThe Israelis remain here in force in
OL,7,Fpart to try to deal with the vast
OL,8,Ftunnel network dug by Hamas, under
OL,9,Fhundreds of metres of pre-fabricated
OL,10,Fconcrete ceiling.
OL,12,FAs recently as last week, Hamas used
OL,13,Fone of these tunnels to spring an
OL,14,Fattack on the IDF. This particular one
OL,15,Fdoubled up as accommodation, and not
OL,16,Fjust for men. The Israelis believe
OL,17,FHamas used this bedroom as a command
OL,18,Fcentre.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1771909410
OL,3,CITV News taken inside Gaza tunnels as
OL,4,CIDF claims Hamas remains active
OL,6,FFor their own security, the Israelis
OL,7,Fwant to destroy all the tunnels. But
OL,8,Fnullifying Hamas' ability to attack is
OL,9,Fa project that will likely delay
OL,10,FGaza's new beginning.
OL,12,FSo this place remains stuck, a bleak,
OL,13,Fdesolate wasteland with a future
OL,14,Fthat's still up in the air.
OL,16,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,17,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,18,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,19,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
